<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l5"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_67_r1l4"><expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>anſen</ex></expan> der wır eẅch <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hıerinn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l6"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr eẅch deſt bas in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> wıſſet ʒu <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l7"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gedenke<ex>n</ex></expan> wıe wır dıe ſache handeln vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_67_r1l8">den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd wıe wır des ʒu rat <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
